Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.14,0:00:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone, Kaleido Star is about to start!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.13,0:00:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When watching Kaleido Star,\Nplease keep the room brightly lit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.90,0:00:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.07,0:00:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm Sora Naegino.\NI came to America all by myself{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with aspirations of joining Kaleido Stage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.35,0:00:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything is new to me, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.02,0:00:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I'm doing my best in the spirit\Nof "try it rather than think about it."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's nothing I can't do if I try,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and if I can do it without\Ntrying, that'll be super lucky.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.77,0:00:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And if I'm gonna do it, I just\Ngotta do it! Gotta! Gotta! That's me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.79,0:00:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well, what would you do\Nif you had to do something super hard?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.64,0:00:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When everyone says that\Nyou don't have a chance?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.32,0:00:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's very tough. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.38,0:00:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But you want to at least\Nbelieve in yourself, you know?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.82,0:00:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So, even in a pinch, let's\Nchange that into an opportunity!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.99,0:01:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's change it! Let's change it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.05,0:01:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yaritai koto wa nani {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.65,0:01:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sou kikareru tabi {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.50,0:01:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aoi sora miageta {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.29,0:01:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kotae wa only my heart {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Honto ni daiji na kotoba\Nwa kantan ni wa iwanai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hikari ga yubisasu\Nbasho e to hashiridasu yo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dakishimetai mono nara\Nnakitai hodo mune ni aru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.32,0:02:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Egakitsuzukete yuku kitto take it someday{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shiroi kumo ga nagareru\Nchiheisen no mukou ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Naranderu mirai wa itsumo soba ni aru kara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.08,0:02:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A doll? A ghost? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Fool. I am \Nthe Spirit of the Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.79,0:02:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing to hear, nothing to hear,\NI'm not hearing any weird voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing to see, nothing to see,\NI'm not seeing anything weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's not there anymore. Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.85,0:02:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, if you can see me,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it means that you were chosen for the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.63,0:03:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's still talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.63,0:03:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora Naegino. Wait, I'm talking back to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora Naegino...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.89,0:03:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like another\Ninteresting star will be born.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.18,0:03:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, a new era is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.04,0:03:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask them to change my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.83,0:03:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.29,0:03:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"My Amazing and Lonely Challenge!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Dorm Supervisor, I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that just now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.94,0:03:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.56,0:04:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teach me that trick you just did!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want you to teach\Nme the trick you just did!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.11,0:04:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I didn't know you were a new student.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am Sora Naegino.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.43,0:04:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that you suddenly opened\Nthe door during my karate practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. So, Dorm Supervisor...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.25,0:04:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please call me Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sarah? As in the diva of Kaleido Stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is that gorgeous diva, Miss Sarah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.64,0:04:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's different from the\Nimage I had in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're Japanese, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm into karate now.\NCan you be my sparring partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All Japanese are black belts, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.57,0:04:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and teach me that trick\Nyou just did too. And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.39,0:05:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew Miss Sarah was like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I couldn't switch my room either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl kissed up to the Boss\Nand cheated her way in, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.71,0:05:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was late for the audition and\Nstill passed. It like, makes me mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.43,0:05:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She kissed up to the Boss to join the troupe?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.26,0:05:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard she's even maneuvered\Nher way onto the stage already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to try three times \Nbefore I was accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The third time's showbiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.44,0:05:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.04,0:05:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about, "In the\Nnick of time's the charm"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot. I screwed up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that expression! You look so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it was just my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:06:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'm a little tired after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're tired, you should\Ntake a shower and go to bed early.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.54,0:06:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. I think I'll\Ndo that. Take a shower and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.46,0:06:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, take your clothes off\Nquickly and take a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.38,0:06:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is here except for you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.55,0:06:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't worry, take your clothes off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You look pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.07,0:06:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, take off your clothes and shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.16,0:06:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.97,0:06:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you treat the\NSpirit of the Stage this way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.71,0:06:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I demand you untie me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least take off the blindfold, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're up early working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:07:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Newcomers shouldn't\Nbe cleaning the stage yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just happened to wake up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's thanks to you that\NI was able to join Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.71,0:07:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking you still have nice legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, everyone, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awfully early.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you like cleaning that much,\Ncan you do our share too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to go to our lessons early.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have talent, but since\NI'm not close to the Boss,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's like the only way for me to\Nappear on stage is by working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So take care of it for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.89,0:07:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a little better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right. I'll just\Nclean this place by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what you'd expect from\NKaleido Stage... it's bigger than it looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.87,0:08:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look tired. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.98,0:08:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a lot of hard work\Nto clean the stage by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You did it by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.34,0:08:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! No, I'm a slowpoke,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it took me longer than the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, if you don't hurry,\Nyou'll be late for your lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.54,0:08:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shoot. See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good luck, Sora. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You still have a long way to go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In these ballet lessons, you will master\Nhow to move your body beautifully,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.99,0:08:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which is essential for grand ceremonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A beautiful body movement, that is--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.35,0:08:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.49,0:08:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:08:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'm late because\NI was cleaning the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, you were also late for\Nthe audition, too, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try harder and catch\Nup on the parts I missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.09,0:09:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then. Now, we're\Ngoing to start the lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, one row at a time, turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to work hard. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.83,0:09:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have any ballet experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be joking.\NYou're the only one without any.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because in order to show\Na beautiful pose on the stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the knowledge of ballet is essential.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.09,0:09:46.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'll think about what you should do,\N so take a short break for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Why was someone like her \Nable to pass the audition?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's so unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's making everyone laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you were on stage
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you couldn't even\Ndo a simple turn like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.64,0:10:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.80,0:10:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll get to go on stage, even if she can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like, it must be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.57,0:10:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I may not be \Nable to even do a turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but someday, I will be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, I'll even be able to do\Namazing routines like Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla's big routine?\NYou mean the Golden Phoenix?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.67,0:10:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seriously think the \NGolden Phoenix is easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.38,0:10:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you think it's like a piece of cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I didn't mean it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you show us your Golden Phoenix?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalos has such confidence in you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Golden Phoenix\Nshould be easy for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Can't you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, I don't\Nacknowledge your existence here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right then. I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.16,0:11:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you that I can \Ndo the Golden Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.84,0:11:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I'll be looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to see it in a week, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.47,0:11:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you can't do it after\Nstating so boldly that you would,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will leave this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.56,0:11:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, let's go to the training room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.44,0:11:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't like you to say\Nsomething like that to a newcomer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't stand Kaleido Stage
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,having someone who can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Golden Phoenix?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.94,0:11:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to borrow a video\Nof Miss Layla if you have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.63,0:11:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is totally reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Golden Phoenix is\Na trick that only a top star
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.67,0:11:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like Miss Layla can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.04,0:11:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's a trick done on the trapeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:11:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, have you ever worked on the trapeze?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.69,0:12:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want everyone to acknowledge me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And for that, I have no choice\Nbut to do the Golden Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Golden Phoenix is\Nperformed by first swinging high
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and spinning your body very fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.67,0:12:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you release the bar,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.88,0:12:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,spread your arms wide like a phoenix,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and catch your partner's bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spinning your body using this\Nspecial bar makes it extremely difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla and Mr. Yuri are using\Nthe training room for their new routine,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.69,0:12:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you'll have to use the\Nactual trapeze on the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a net, but it's still dangerous,\Nsince the trapeze is pretty high.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do I need to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.09,0:12:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, you need to practice\Nswinging your body back and forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After gaining enough momentum,\Nyou'll jump to the bar on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.63,0:13:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you fall, make sure you\Nland on your back. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have enough\Nmomentum! One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I never knew just swinging \Nwould be this hard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.72,0:13:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I will do it no matter what!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that I ended up\Nkeeping you here until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.37,0:13:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's for you, I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.84,0:13:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Mr. Policeman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing so early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.06,0:14:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was practicing on the trapeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me when you'll be on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your number one fan, got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.81,0:14:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mr. Policeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to see if you're worthy\Nenough to be Sora's boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it all wrong! He's not\Nmy boyfriend or anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.43,0:14:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.11,0:14:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, Sora, good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.49,0:14:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I really have to work hard, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:49.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--Not anything like that. \NNot anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Or I'll end up leaving this place\Nbefore I even get to be on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:51.28,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--Not anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.02,0:14:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ken, keep me company again tonight, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.34,0:15:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you practicing all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, because if I don't work hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.55,0:15:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something you\Ncan do just by working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.39,0:15:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you give up\Nand apologize to Miss Layla?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave up on joining Kaleido Stage earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.90,0:15:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because I missed the audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But somehow I managed to get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.21,0:15:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I really want to stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.11,0:15:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't ever want to give up again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.52,0:15:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think that hurts,\Nyou still have a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.64,0:15:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reverse Chariot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.78,0:15:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card indicates that things will\Nend in failure and you will taste defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.44,0:15:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, even if the results\Nof a fortune telling are bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.61,0:15:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the future can be changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on that person's efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, in order to gain the muscle\Nstrength to perform various tricks,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.22,0:16:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you have to eat a low-fat \Nand high-protein diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.44,0:16:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's working really hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.56,0:16:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Sora. Next, you have\Nto do it while you're spinning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.36,0:16:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We brought you something to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you haven't eaten anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.29,0:16:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.71,0:16:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.53,0:16:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you liked it. Please have all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.02,0:16:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.02,0:16:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I recommend this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot pepper drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:16:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll give you energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.46,0:17:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anna, Mia, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.44,0:17:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Sora. It's all because\NI mentioned the Golden Phoenix...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because now, I have a chance to prove myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At first, I thought you were accepted\Nbecause you kissed up to the Boss,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess that wasn't the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.31,0:17:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the bandage on your hand is coming loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me fix it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.34,0:17:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck. We're rooting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.86,0:17:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swing the bar back and forth. Spin,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.15,0:17:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Sora okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's doing image training.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.61,0:17:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's picturing the image of\Nthe perfected routine in her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.28,0:17:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.78,0:17:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.27,0:17:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore... Well, in other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.37,0:17:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm listening to the lecture.\NPlease don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.62,0:17:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy for you to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.22,0:18:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mr. Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.18,0:18:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world were you\Nlooking at when you jumped?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.55,0:18:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no Juliet who is not\Nalways gazing at her Romeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why you are not Juliet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.83,0:18:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not completely in \Nthe character of Juliet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So close! She almost made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.68,0:18:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe she managed to\Ndo all this in such a short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.63,0:19:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she can just grab the bar now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she still can't maintain\Na beautiful pose in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before she catches the bar,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what she's doing can't be\Ncalled the Golden Phoenix.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.56,0:19:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.77,0:19:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to perfect it by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.20,0:19:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't perfect it after all,\Nbut you did do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.98,0:19:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no knowing yet.\NThe real test is tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't given up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to see what kind of\NGolden Phoenix she'll show us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.56,0:19:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to do it. I need \Nto believe in myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bar should not be my aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My aim should be my love, Romeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I can be Juliet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.60,0:20:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Golden Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.62,0:20:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.42,0:20:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.04,0:20:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:20:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:20:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't get the last part right,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.42,0:21:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that was definitely the Golden Phoenix.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.92,0:21:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I have to acknowledge you this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.12,0:21:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.57,0:21:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, you can stay at Kaleido Stage now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.32,0:21:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.33,0:21:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad for you, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.11,0:21:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can stay at Kaleido Stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.29,0:21:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.89,0:21:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you happy now that you\Ncan stay at Kaleido Stage, Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.59,0:21:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, I think the three of you\Nshould take a bath together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.74,0:21:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that true friendship\Nstarts with sharing a bath together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.31,0:21:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are concerned about me, do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.24,0:21:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.83,0:21:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! What are you doing, Sora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well. This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.15,0:21:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.95,0:21:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.84,0:22:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a Japanese comedy\Nroutine I've heard of called "tsukkomi."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.22,0:22:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.96,0:22:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys can't see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.46,0:22:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.04,0:22:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're throwing a party? We can't have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.08,0:22:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dorm Supervisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.40,0:22:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not allowed to have a party?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.18,0:22:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not, unless you invite me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.03,0:22:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the rule at this dormitory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.43,0:22:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sarah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.55,0:22:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sarah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.84,0:22:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.13,0:22:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's have some fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.04,0:22:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The image I had of her...
